divs: Sighting DetailsDuring a sighting of several meteorites my son say's he say a object that looked like a meteorite but stopped for 2 seconds and then moved at several sharp angles, original coming down then made sharp angled immediate turns toward the opposite direction of the meteorites and then disappeared. My son was outside at a friends house in the backyard playing on a trampoline when the took a break laid on it and looked up. He say's what drew his attention was at first he thought it was meteorite but when it behaved strangely he took note of it, He called a strange shooting star.
